What is the structure of your dataset?¶

the dataframe at the first (before cleaning or indexing it ) contains 113937 rows with 81 columns, each row is about a loan, most variables are numeric but there are some data that seems to be categorical like prosper rating numeric , prosper rating (alpha) 7 , prosperscore 11 unique value , employment status , Isborrowerhomeowner,currently in group , also I observed that many colums say that the date is after 2009 so I dropped all the entries that is before 2009 after this modification the data became 84853 entries or rows

What is/are the main feature(s) of interest in your dataset?¶

my main interest here is LoanStatus,borrowerAPR,Borrowerrate and how they are affected by the other variables that I am going to investigate

What features in the dataset do you think will help support your investigation into your feature(s) of interest?¶

my initial intuition that the features that I will need to investigate is ProsperRating (numeric),ProsperRating (Alpha),ProsperScore,CurrentlyIngroup,EmploymentStatus,EmploymentStatusDuration,IsBorrowerHomeowner,CurrentDelinquencies,DebtToIncomeRatio
